{"tid":600711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 機場對開駁船沉沒　40人跳船逃","createTime":"2018-03-21T14:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T16:31:48.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2802c2739cf77a1b52c75f8f057ff2788c114d1","tid":600711,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"機場對開海面發生沉船意外，晚上8時許，一艘船隻在機場以北疑入水沉沒，期間多艘船隻途經，船員見狀慌忙協助救人。據了解，涉事船隻為機場第三跑道工程的載人接駁船隻，當時沉船上約有40人，船身沉沒一半，幸船上全部人及時跳船逃生。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，消防處接報後，出動一艘消防輪及一艘潛水消防船趕赴現場救援，由於恐怕有人被困，消防潛水蛙人正在海面及下沉的船隻內搜救。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180321/mobile/bkn-20180321215306628-0321_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180321%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180321215306628-0321_00822_001.html&d=66jwbLEEruHbFfMAf1JUasmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7860a546\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180321/mobile/bkn-20180321215306628-0321_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe59b3ae03a40fb09a00679b9d04e39364d9fdc1","tid":600711,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f2a43aa6199de509892c21c13bf6f51e9a5ee3","tid":600711,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f087a25d1e05a631c96864e8b05304eee749aadd","tid":600711,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60f2a43aa6199de509892c21c13bf6f51e9a5ee3","tid":600711,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4660a4967f18215666ef9d6c9844e7ccc1faa8","tid":600711,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"